                Estimates the value at the specified point.                
                <@param>
                    m point the point for which the value is estimated.                    
                </@param>
                <@param>
                    m pointValues the point-value entries.                    
                </@param>
                <@return>
                    n the estimated value at the specified point.                    
                </@return>
